Class HDBOfficerRegistration

java.lang.Object
com.group6.btoproject.HDBOfficerRegistration
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class HDBOfficerRegistration extends Object implements Serializable
Represents a HDB Officer's request to register as an officer for this project. Note: Due to how the statuses are inferred and how registrations are managed by BTOProject, this class should only be mutated by BTOProject to avoid weird application states. See HDBOfficerRegistrationStatus for possible statuses.
